<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>You've Been Outbid</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #f59e0b;">⚠️ You've Been Outbid</h1>
  
  <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
  
  <p>Someone has placed a higher bid on <strong>{{productName}}</strong>.</p>
  
  <div style="background: #fef3c7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p><strong>Your Bid:</strong> Rp {{yourBid}}</p>
    <p><strong>New Highest Bid:</strong> Rp {{newHighestBid}}</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>Bid again to win this item!</p>
  
  <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">© {{year}} TCG Store. All rights reserved.</p>
</body>
</html>